Hello! My name is Sarah, and I'm a customer service representative from RT 6 Boozers. How can I assist you today?

Hi Sarah! I wanted to ask about the happy hour specials.

Of course! Our happy hour runs every weekday from four PM to six PM, with fifty percent off all drinks. May I start by getting your name?

Sure! My name is James.

Thank you, James! It's great to meet you. Could you also provide me with your phone number, please?

It's five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Thank you for that! And just to ensure we have everything correct, could you also give me your email address?

Absolutely, it's james.smith at example dot com.

Perfect, thank you, James! We’ll make sure to keep you updated with any special events and offers through your email.

That sounds great, thank you for your help!

You're very welcome! Thank you for your time, James. Have a wonderful day and enjoy your time at RT 6 Boozers!
